subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Maria Kirilenko avoided an upset and reached the quarterfinals of the Cincinnati Women’s Open with a 1-6, 6-2, 7-5 win over the qualifier Stephanie Dubois. Kirilenko will play Sabine Lisicki, who beat Camille Pin.
